          It is definitely in the top 10 classic places list to visit here, even if you come for 24 hours. It’s in the heart of downtown Portland (just 25min from our home, so there’s no excuse). They have everything. I mean EVERYTHING.
          Get yourself a little PDX souvenir (other than the wonderful wedding memories we know you’ll have in your Instagram).
        </p>
